      • filter

        public Compressor filter(java.util.function.BiPredicate<java.lang.String,java.io.File> filter)
        Allows filtering entries being added to the archive. Please note that the second parameter of a filter (File) could be null when the filter is applied to an entry not present on a disk - e.g. via addFile(String, byte[]).
